    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor Fire Starter Necklace is a must-have emergency tool. Each necklace comes with a serrated metal fire starter striker so you can ensure you have access to a heat and light source in case of an outdoor emergency. The necklace also comes with a mini ferrocerium rod that can be used with the striker to easily create sparks, allowing you to start a fire without any other tools. It will work at any altitude and in any weather condition, so you can rest assured you’ll have access to heat rain, or shine. The striker features a serrated blade that will assist with striking the mini ferro rod to create flame sparks. It can also be used as a sturdy cutting device in a pinch! The necklace itself is constructed of durable 550 paracord and can be adjusted for custom comfort</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Paracord Necklace Fire Starter Striker Tool Blade (Many Styles)</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor Fire Starter Necklace is a must-have emergency tool. Each necklace comes with a serrated metal fire starter striker so you can ensure you have access to a heat and light source in case of an outdoor emergency.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>EMERGENCY FIRE STARTER – The ASR Outdoor Fire Starter Necklace is a must-have emergency tool. Each necklace comes with a serrated metal fire starter striker so you can ensure you have access to a heat and light source in case of an outdoor emergency.</li>\n    <li>MINI FERRO ROD – The necklace also comes with a mini ferrocerium rod that can be used with the striker to easily create sparks, allowing you to start a fire without any other tools. It will work at any altitude and in any weather condition, so you can rest assured you’ll have access to heat rain or shine.</li>\n    <li>SERRATED BLADE – The striker features a serrated blade that will assist with striking the mini ferro rod to create flame sparks. It can also be used as a sturdy cutting device in a pinch!</li>\n    <li>ADJUSTABLE NECKLACE – The necklace itself is constructed of durable 550 paracord and can be adjusted for custom comfort. It has an overall length of 16”, and can be taken apart to double the length of paracord in an emergency.</li>\n    <li>HIGH VISIBILITY ORANGE – The paracord necklace comes in a bright-orange color, making it easy to spot in the outdoors If you accidentally drop it during use. This is a great EDC, camping, hiking or backpacking emergency tool!</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/ASROPNOSS2_para_striker_necklace_ORG_srr_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"The ASR Outdoor Fire Starter Necklace is a must-have emergency tool\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASROPNOSS2</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058488176</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The necklace also comes with a mini ferrocerium rod that can be used with the striker to easily create sparks, allowing you to start a fire without any other tools. It will work at any altitude and in any weather condition, so you can rest a